<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="rob-vt">rob <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɒb/    美 /rɑːb/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>劫掠；抢劫：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They robbed the rich to help the poor. 
他们劫富济贫。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="rob-sb-of-sth">rob sb of sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>抢走某人的某物：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The young man robbed her of her bag. 
那个年轻人抢走了她的包。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>robber /'rɒbə(r)/ n <br />
robbery /'rɒbəri/ n   </p></div>